<dl id="n12079d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12079d">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12079d"> 79(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Uter Pendragon</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">C&apos;est &agrave; cause du dragon expliqu&eacute; par Merlin qu&apos;il fut nomm&eacute; Penn-dragon ou <i>Chef-dragon</i>, &agrave; en croire les Armoricains. <br><font color="green">[It was because Merlin had explained this dragon that <mark>Uter was called Penn-dragon</mark> or <i>Chief- dragon</i>, if we can trust the Armoricans]</font> <small> [TLMM]Th&eacute;odore-Claude Hersart, Vicomte de La Villemarqu&eacute;, <cite a>Myrdhinn, ou l'enchanteur Merlin</cite></a> (1862) 114</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
